snippet.title: Best VGM 918 - Tales of Graces - Crush that Steel!
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1846 - https://youtu.be/f0UzNWcwC30

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Wii / PS3
Tales of Graces (2010)
Crush that Steel! (Bashis Base)
Motoi Sakuraba
